## skillIcons.ts

**Location:** `src/data/skillIcons.ts`

**Purpose:** Map skill display names to `{ path: string; title: string }` for SkillsCard. Use `simple-icons` package for most icons; add manual SVG paths for icons not in the package (e.g., AWS, Azure, PowerShell).

**Export:** `skillIconMap: Record<string, { path: string; title: string }>`

## Adding New Data

1. Define interface in appropriate file in `src/data/`
2. Export the array or object
3. Import in the bento component that renders it (e.g., CertificationsCard imports from certificates.ts)
4. Add or wire the section in BentoGrid if it is a new section type
